rong>\", \"fields.sw-color-danger\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-danger</strong>\", \"fields.sw-logo-desktop\": \"Displayed for viewports of above 991px <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>sw-logo-desktop</strong>\", \"fields.sw-logo-favicon\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-logo-favicon</strong>\", \"fields.zen-input-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-input-color</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-success\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-success</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-warning\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-warning</strong>\", \"fields.zen-container-bg\": \"Leave the field empty or enter \'transparent\' to make the container backgrounds invisible. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-container-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-footer-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-header-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-header-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-header-style\": \"With this selection, the representation of the header can be set to a single-line or multi-line header. With a single-line header, the main navigation is shown in one line with the logo and the shop navigation. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-header-style</strong>\", \"fields.zen-layout-style\": \"boxed = Boxed <br> full-width-boxed = Full Width Boxed <br> full-width-header = Full Width Header <br> full-width = Full Width <br><br>Sets the basic layout width of the shop: Boxed = Limited width; Full Width Boxed = elements limited width and backgrounds fit to browser width; FullWidthHeader = Header elements fit to browser edge all other content have a limited width, backgrounds fit to browser edge; FullWidth = elements and backgrounds fit to browser border <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-layout-style</strong>\", \"fields.zen-search-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-search-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-search-style\": \"The search can be displayed in the default (open) or expandable and overlay. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-search-style</strong>\", \"fields.sw-headline-color\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-headline-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-header-height\": \"in px - Set the height of the main header element for bigger viewports. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-header-height</strong>\", \"fields.zen-layout-bg-img\": \"Background image of the body. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-layout-bg-img</strong>\", \"fields.zen-logo-position\": \"Place the logo inside the header. The other elements such as search and shop navigation are also automatically realigned. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-logo-position</strong>\", \"fields.zen-search-border\": \"If the search appearance is set to <strong>\'Overlay\'</strong>, the border-color is used as underline color. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-search-border</strong>\", \"fields.zen-sticky-header\": \"The header will be stick to the top when you scroll to bottom of the page. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-sticky-header</strong>\", \"fields.zen-top-bar-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-top-bar-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-top-bar-style\": \"In addition to the top bar that can be folded in or out, it can also be displayed as an offcanvas element like the shopping cart. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-top-bar-style</strong>\", \"fields.zen-breadcrumbs-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-breadcrumbs-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-category-image\": \"If active, the category picture is inserted as a background in the first section of the set experience world. Categories without a category image represent the background image inserted in the shopping experience as a fallback. <br><br>[≡] This option can be individually overwritten in each category. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-category-image</strong>\", \"fields.zen-input-focus-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-input-focus-bg</strong>\", \"fields.sw-background-color\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-background-color</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-buy-button\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-buy-button</strong>\", \"fields.sw-font-family-base\": \"1. Visit https://fonts.google.com<br><br> 2. Choose font <br><br>3. Enter font name: Font embedding is composed automatically by font name to the embedding link - Replace spaces in font names with <strong>+</strong>. <br><br>Example:<br><strong>Roboto Condensed</strong> becomes <strong>Roboto+Condensed</strong> <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>sw-font-family-base</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-logo-col\": \"[!] If display as column: Column width of the footer logo column. 12 columns give 100% width. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-footer-logo-col</strong>\", \"fields.zen-input-font-size\": \"in px <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-input-font-size</strong>\", \"fields.zen-product-tabs-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-product-tabs-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-search-focus-bg\": \"[!] If the search appearance is set to <strong>\'Overlay\'</strong>, the hover background color is not used. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-search-focus-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-bottom-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-footer-bottom-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-light-text-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-light-text-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-logo-size-mobile\": \"in % - Logo size in % for smaller viewports <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-logo-size-mobile</strong>\", \"fields.zen-top-bar-hover-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-top-bar-hover-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-breadcrumbs-align\": \"[!] Note that the orientation of the breadcrumbs of the Breadcrumbs-experience-element is not affected by this. These have their own configuration for alignment in the element settings. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-breadcrumbs-align</strong>\", \"fields.zen-breadcrumbs-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-breadcrumbs-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-custom-col\": \"[!] If active in plugin settings: Column width of the custom column. 12 columns give 100% width. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-footer-custom-col</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-logo-order\": \"[!] If display as column: Sort order of the columns (numbers from 1-12) The higher the number, the further back the column is shown. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-footer-logo-order</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-social-col\": \"[!] If display as column:Column width of the social media icons column. 12 columns give 100% width. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-footer-social-col</strong>\", \"fields.zen-input-focus-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-input-focus-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-input-font-weight\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-input-font-weight</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-brand-primary\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-brand-primary</strong>\", \"fields.zen-category-filter-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-category-filter-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-category-filter-mb\": \"in px - Margin bottom of filter items in sidebar. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-category-filter-mb</strong>\", \"fields.zen-category-filter-pv\": \"in px - Padding of filter items in sidebar. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-category-filter-pv</strong>\", \"fields.zen-font-family-import\": \"If active, the fonts are implemented by Google Fonts (fonts.google.com). An additional note in your privacy policy regarding the use of Google Fonts may be necessary. Deactivate this option if you want to host the fonts yourself and no connection to the Google servers should be established. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-font-family-import</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-hotline-col\": \"[!] If display as column: Column width of the hotline column. 12 columns give 100% width. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-footer-hotline-col</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-hover-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-footer-hover-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-logo-col-xl\": \"[!] If display as column: Column width of the footer logo column. 12 columns give 100% width. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-footer-logo-col-xl</strong>\", \"fields.zen-header-padding-top\": \"in px - Set the padding top of the main header element for bigger viewports. <br><br><br>Variable: <stron